text: Here Before is the fifth studio album by the American rock band the Feelies. It was released on April 12, 2011, on Bar/None. ==Reception== This album received positive reviews from Michael Hann, Stuart Berman, and Mark Deming also earning a score of 73 out of a possible 100 based on 17 critical reviews by Metacritic, indicating generally positive feedback. ==Track listing== ==References== Category:2011 albums Category:The Feelies albums Category:Bar/None Records albums
title: Here Before (album)
